oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: 1st Annual Cowboy Ball (2003)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Cowboys; Festivals; Fund raising; Horses; Split fountain printing; Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (burgundy and split fountain, red to yellow, on white) announcing the First Annual Cowboy Ball, benefiting the Angel Heart Farm, hosted by Luke Perry and featuring music by Lee Roy Parnell and Deuces Wild at The Factory on October 24. Poster features a woodcut of a cowboy on a horse.
